{"metadata":{"title":"setUser:emails:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"emails:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}]}],"name":"userId"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings."}]}],"name":"emails"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Atomically associates a user ID with multiple email addresses and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"confirmation when the operation completes. This is the recommended method","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for user identification during authentication flows.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle OAuth login with full user setup:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class OAuthLoginHandler {","","    func handleOAuthCallback(_ authResult: OAuthResult,","                            completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        \/\/ Extract user info from OAuth result","        let userId = authResult.userId","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primaryEmail = authResult.email {","            emails.append(primaryEmail)","        }","        if let verifiedEmails = authResult.verifiedEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: verifiedEmails.filter { $0 != authResult.email })","        }","","        \/\/ Set user and emails with confirmation","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(userId, emails: emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.error(\"User setup failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                completion(.failure(error))","                return","            }","","            \/\/ User is now fully identified - set profile tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"oauth_provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"has_profile_picture\": authResult.profilePictureURL != nil,","                \"locale\": authResult.locale ?? Locale.current.identifier,","                \"first_login\": !self.hasExistingSession(for: userId)","            ])","","            Analytics.track(\"oauth_login_complete\", properties: [","                \"provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:completion:":{"title":"setUser:emails:completion:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:completion:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}